title: Initial inquiry call
description: Discussed program options and admission requirements. Parent very interested in STEM track.

title: Application materials sent
description: Sent complete application packet including forms, requirements checklist, and deadline information.

title: Parent-teacher conference
description: Discussed academic progress and extracurricular participation. Student excelling in math and science.

title: Application status update
description: Student submitted partial application. Missing recommendation letters and transcript.

title: Follow-up on missing documents
description: Contacted parent about outstanding application materials. Provided extension until February 5th.

title: Complete application received
description: All materials submitted. Strong academic record with 3.8 GPA. Leadership experience in student government.

title: Academic planning session
description: Reviewed course selections for sophomore year. Student interested in advanced placement classes.

title: Acceptance notification sent
description: Congratulations email sent with enrollment packet and next steps for fall semester.

title: Campus tour scheduled
description: Family requested campus visit. Scheduled for February 10th at 2 PM with admissions counselor.

title: Graduation planning meeting
description: Reviewed credit requirements and college application timeline. Student on track for early graduation.

title: Application assistance call
description: Helped family navigate online application portal. Addressed questions about financial aid options.

title: Scholarship information sent
description: Provided details about merit-based scholarship opportunities. Application deadline March 1st.

title: Extracurricular update
description: Student joined robotics team and debate club. Showing strong engagement in school activities.

title: Final application review
description: Excellent application with strong essays and recommendations. Candidate for early admission consideration.

title: Academic progress review
description: Mid-year grades review. Student maintaining honor roll status with 3.9 GPA.
